Class ObjectSocketImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • jsocket.socket.SocketImpl
      • jsocket.socket.StringSocketImpl
        • jsocket.socket.ObjectSocketImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ObjectSocket, Socket, StringSocket

    public class ObjectSocketImpl
extends StringSocketImpl
implements ObjectSocket
    Abstracts jsocket.socket.StringSocket implemntations to handle complex objects instead of strings It is suggested that implementation extend jsocket.socket.StringSocketImpl Default implementation
    Version:
    0.1.0
    Author:
    Will Czifro
